Wilma P. STRICKLAND v. Gilda GRAY, whose True Name is Maryanna Michalska, and Columbia Pictures Corporation. No. 4923. United States Court of' Appeals, Tenth Circuit. May 26, 1954. No appearance for appellant. Hodges, Silverstein, Hodges & Harrington, Denver, Colo., and David H. Morris, Colorado Springs, Colo., for ap-pellees.

Before PHILLLIPS Chief Judge, and BRATTON and HUXMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Docketed and dismissed on motion of appellees, for failure of appellant diligently to prosecute.
